  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the equivalence or not of diagnosis ability of
      oesophagal videocapsul versus oeso-gastro-duodenal fiber endoscopy in the screening of
      oesophagal varix.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
